room_title: Escape room "Bust the Bank" by Count:down Escape Games in West Palm Beach
room_description: You and your partner are ready for one last heist and you have chosen one of the most difficult banks to rob. Armed with a sophisticated laser system and one of the most complex vault doors ever seen, this one is not going to be easy. You only have 30 minutes, so work fast and exit the bank before the police arrive or you're busted!
